description:
Vowing to post something happy in my feed each week.

I know these are “crazy,” “unprecedented,” “scary,” —whatever adjective you want to use — times.

But these are also the times of OUR LIVES.

I know I get worked up. I say my piece. I stand up for what I believe. Heck yes I do! But I also LOVE MY FAMILY and FIND JOY in the ONE LIFE GOD GAVE ME.

There are no do overs. I won’t let a governor mandating me to live his way cause me anxiety or stress that makes me live less, smile less, enjoy less.

There’s gotta be some good out there ... let’s talk about it!🖤
